<div class="content" name="CAL" uuid="280e1934-7a46-4e56-a244-9a0c092d9c8d"><p>The CAL structure defines a counted array of 32-bit unsigned
integers.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct tagCAL {
   unsigned long cElems;
   [size_is(cElems )] long* pElems;
 } CAL;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>cElems:</b>  MUST be set to the total
number of elements of the array.</p><p><b>pElems:</b>  An array of 32-bit unsigned
integers.</p></div>